data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home available for sale in South Temecula. Bright and open floor plan.  The upstairs bedrooms feature closets and ceiling fans. Located on a cul-de -sac, in the wonderful community of Paloma del sol.   Newly installed carpet throughout the upstairs.  The yard is private with a large patio area.    Walkable to several community parks and recreation center. Paloma del Sol is well known for its over 100 acres of parks, walking trails, and green belts. The area also features multiple swimming pools, parks, basketball and tennis courts along with much more. Excellent temecula schools as well!  Set up a time to see the home today!
